title: Jane Bunnett and Maqueque break barriers and borders with jazz
tags: Jane Bunnett and Maqueque Cuban jazz
fulltitle: Jane Bunnett and Maqueque break barriers and borders with jazz
description:
Five-time Juno Award winner Jane Bunnett has joined forces with five young Cuban musicians to form a border-breaking jazz supergroup called Jane Bunnett and Maqueque. http://cbc.ca/1.5359507
